---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Contact Capital Wealth Advisors | Schedule Consultation | Lehi, UT"
description: "Schedule a consultation with Capital Wealth Advisors in Lehi, Utah. Call 801.210.2800 or email info@capitalwealth.com. Initial consultations are complimentary."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { name: "Contact", url: "/contact/" }
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Contact Capital Wealth Advisors</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Ready to take control of your retirement planning? Let's start the conversation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact Information -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
            <!-- Contact Details -->
            <div>
                <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
                <p class="text-lg">We're here to answer your retirement planning questions and help you create a financial strategy that works for your unique situation.</p>
                
                <div class="mt-xl">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3 class="text-accent">Schedule a Consultation</h3>
                        <p class="mb-lg">Initial consultations are complimentary for qualified families with $500K+ in retirement savings.</p>
                        
                        <div class="hero-cta">
                            <a href="tel:{{ site.phone }}" class="btn btn-primary">Call {{ site.phone }}</a>
                            <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="btn btn-secondary">Email Us</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mt-lg">
                    <h3>Office Location</h3>
                    <p>{{ site.address.street }}<br>
                       {{ site.address.city }}, {{ site.address.state }} {{ site.address.zip }}</p>
                    
                    <h3 class="mt-lg">Office Hours</h3>
                    <p>Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM<br>
                       Saturday: By appointment<br>
                       Sunday: Closed</p>
                    
                    <h3 class="mt-lg">Emergency Contact</h3>
                    <p>For urgent matters outside business hours, please call our main number and leave a detailed message. We will respond as quickly as possible.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Contact Form -->
            <div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Request a Consultation</h3>
                    <p>Fill out the form below and we'll contact you within one business day to schedule your complimentary consultation.</p>
                    
                    <form class="mt-lg" id="contact-form">
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <label for="name" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Full Name *</label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid var(--bg-light); border-radius: var(--border-radius); background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1rem;">
                        </div>
                        
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <label for="email" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Email Address *</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid var(--bg-light); border-radius: var(--border-radius); background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1rem;">
                        </div>
                        
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <label for="phone" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Phone Number *</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid var(--bg-light); border-radius: var(--border-radius); background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1rem;">
                        </div>
                        
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <label for="savings" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Retirement Savings Amount</label>
                            <select id="savings" name="savings" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid var(--bg-light); border-radius: var(--border-radius); background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1rem;">
                                <option value="">Please select</option>
                                <option value="$250K - $500K">$250K - $500K</option>
                                <option value="$500K - $1M">$500K - $1M</option>
                                <option value="$1M - $2M">$1M - $2M</option>
                                <option value="$2M+">$2M+</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <label for="retirement-timeline" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Retirement Timeline</label>
                            <select id="retirement-timeline" name="retirement-timeline" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid var(--bg-light); border-radius: var(--border-radius); background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1rem;">
                                <option value="">Please select</option>
                                <option value="Already retired">Already retired</option>
                                <option value="1-2 years">1-2 years</option>
                                <option value="3-5 years">3-5 years</option>
                                <option value="5-10 years">5-10 years</option>
                                <option value="10+ years">10+ years</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                            <label for="questions" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Questions or Comments</label>
                            <textarea id="questions" name="questions" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us about your retirement planning goals or any specific questions you have..." style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid var(--bg-light); border-radius: var(--border-radius); background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1rem; resize: vertical;"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Honeypot -->
                        <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;"><input type="text" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off"></div>
                        
                        <button type="submit" id="submit-btn" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" style="width: 100%;">Request Consultation</button>
                        <div id="form-status" style="margin-top: 12px; text-align: center; font-weight: 500;"></div>
                    </form>
                    
                    <script>
                    document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
                      e.preventDefault();
                      var btn = document.getElementById('submit-btn');
                      var status = document.getElementById('form-status');
                      
                      // Honeypot check
                      if (this.querySelector('[name="website"]').value) return;
                      
                      btn.disabled = true;
                      btn.textContent = 'Sending...';
                      status.textContent = '';
                      
                      try {
                        var res = await fetch('/api/submit-lead', {
                          method: 'POST',
                          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                          body: JSON.stringify({
                            name: document.getElementById('name').value,
                            email: document.getElementById('email').value,
                            phone: document.getElementById('phone').value,
                            savings: document.getElementById('savings').value,
                            retirementTimeline: document.getElementById('retirement-timeline').value,
                            questions: document.getElementById('questions').value
                          })
                        });
                        var data = await res.json();
                        if (res.ok) {
                          status.style.color = '#2d8a4e';
                          status.textContent = data.message || "Thank you! We'll be in touch within one business day.";
                          this.reset();
                        } else {
                          status.style.color = '#c0392b';
                          status.textContent = data.error || 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
                        }
                      } catch (err) {
                        status.style.color = '#c0392b';
                        status.textContent = 'Network error. Please try again or call us at 801.210.2800.';
                      }
                      btn.disabled = false;
                      btn.textContent = 'Request Consultation';
                    });
                    </script>
                    
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-md">By submitting this form, you agree to be contacted by Capital Wealth Advisors regarding your retirement planning needs. We respect your privacy and will never share your information.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- What to Expect -->
<section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-xl">What to Expect in Your Consultation</h2>
        
        <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="process-step">
                <div class="process-number">1</div>
                <h3>Discovery</h3>
                <p>We'll discuss your current financial situation, retirement goals, and any concerns you have about your future.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
                <div class="process-number">2</div>
                <h3>Analysis</h3>
                <p>We'll review your existing accounts, investment strategy, and identify opportunities for improvement.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
                <div class="process-number">3</div>
                <h3>Recommendations</h3>
                <p>Based on our analysis, we'll provide initial recommendations and explain how we can help optimize your retirement plan.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-xl">
            <div class="card" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h3 class="text-accent">No Pressure, Just Information</h3>
                <p>Our initial consultation is educational. We'll provide valuable insights whether or not you decide to work with us. Our goal is to help you make informed decisions about your financial future.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

