                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="text-accent">Virtual Services Available</h3>
                <p>We also serve clients nationwide through virtual meetings and digital planning tools. Our services include:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <li>Video consultations</li>
                    <li>Digital document sharing</li>
                    <li>Online portfolio access</li>
                    <li>Phone and email support</li>
